dence of Sigma_SFR on metallicity\nover the entire range of gas surface densities, and can also explain part of\nthe scatter in the observations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 16 Sep 2011 19:28:56 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 27 Sep 2011 10:06:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-03-19"}
